lead_paragraph: If Leicester's rise to the top of English soccer is the most bewildering aspect of this chaotic season in the Premier League, then the implosion of Chelsea runs a close second.

headline.print_headline: Chelsea's Implosion Leaves Incoming Conte With Tough Job
